@startuml level2_infotainment
!theme plain

title Level 2: Infotainment Domain Architecture\nUser Interface and Entertainment Systems

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor LightSalmon
    BorderColor DarkOrange
    ArrowColor DarkBlue
}

package "Infotainment Domain" {

    component "IVI\n(In-Vehicle Infotainment)" as IVI {
        portin p_user_input
        portin p_vehicle_data
        portin p_adas_warnings
        portout p_display_data
        portout p_ambient_light
        portout p_media_control

        [Media Player]
        [Navigation System]
        [Ambient Lighting Manager]
        [User Profile Manager]
        [Connectivity Service]
        [Voice Recognition]
    }

    component "CLU\n(Cluster Unit)" as CLU {
        portin p_vehicle_speed
        portin p_engine_rpm
        portin p_warnings
        portout p_display_output

        [Speed Display]
        [RPM Display]
        [Warning Lights]
        [Trip Computer]
    }

    component "HUD\n(Head-Up Display)" as HUD {
        portin p_speed_data
        portin p_navigation_data
        portout p_hud_projection

        [Speed Projection]
        [Navigation Arrows]
        [ADAS Warnings]
    }

    component "TMU\n(Telematics Unit)" as TMU {
        portin p_vehicle_status
        portout p_connectivity_data
        portout p_remote_control

        [LTE/5G Modem]
        [Remote Diagnostics]
        [OTA Updates]
        [Emergency Call (eCall)]
    }

    component "CUBIS\n(Connected User Box)" as CUBIS {
        portin p_user_device
        portout p_connectivity_status

        [Smartphone Integration]
        [Wireless Charging]
        [Device Management]
    }
}

cloud "CAN-HS #2\n500 kbps" as CAN2

' IVI Messages (Project-Specific)
IVI --> CAN2 : **IVI_AmbientLight (0x400)**\n• Ambient_Light_R/G/B\n• Brightness (%)\n• Theme_Package\nCycle: 100ms, QM

IVI --> CAN2 : **IVI_Profile (0x410)**\n• Profile_ID\n• Scenario_ID\n• Scenario_Params\nCycle: 1000ms (Event), QM

IVI --> CAN2 : **IVI_MediaInfo**\n• Media_Source\n• Track_Info\n• Volume_Level\nCycle: 500ms

CAN2 --> IVI : **LDWS_LKAS11**\n• ADAS Warnings\n(via Gateway)

CAN2 --> IVI : **EMS16**\n• Vehicle_Speed, RPM\n(via Gateway)

' CLU Messages
CLU --> CAN2 : **CLU11**\n• Display_Mode\n• Warning_Status\n• Trip_Data\nCycle: 100ms

CAN2 --> CLU : **EMS16**\n• Vehicle_Speed, RPM\n(via Gateway)

CAN2 --> CLU : **ESP12**\n• Stability_Warnings\n(via Gateway)

' HUD Messages
HUD --> CAN2 : **HUD11**\n• HUD_Active\n• Brightness_Level\nCycle: 100ms

CAN2 --> HUD : **EMS16**\n• Vehicle_Speed\n(via Gateway)

CAN2 --> HUD : **IVI_NavData**\n• Navigation_Arrows

' TMU Messages
TMU --> CAN2 : **TMU11**\n• Connectivity_Status\n• Signal_Strength\n• OTA_Status\nCycle: 1000ms

' CUBIS Messages
CUBIS --> CAN2 : **CUBIS11**\n• Device_Connected\n• Charging_Status\nCycle: 500ms

component "CGW\n(Central Gateway)" as CGW
CAN2 --> CGW : Route to CAN-HS #1, CAN-LS
CGW --> CAN2 : Vehicle Data, ADAS Warnings

cloud "CAN-LS\n125 kbps" as CAN3
CGW --> CAN3 : **IVI_AmbientLight**\n(to BCM)

note right of IVI
  **IVI Key Functions**
  • Media playback (Audio/Video)
  • Navigation (GPS, maps)
  • Ambient lighting control
  • User profile management
  • Smartphone connectivity
  • Voice recognition

  **Safety Level**: QM
  **Cycle Time**: 100-1000ms
  **Display**: 10-12 inch touchscreen
end note

note right of CLU
  **CLU Key Functions**
  • Speed display (analog/digital)
  • RPM display (tachometer)
  • Warning lights (engine, ABS, etc.)
  • Trip computer (fuel, distance)
  • Gear position indicator

  **Safety Level**: QM
  **Cycle Time**: 100ms
  **Display**: 7-12 inch TFT
end note

note bottom of CAN2
  **Infotainment CAN Messages**

  User Interface (100-500ms):
  • IVI_AmbientLight: RGB control
  • IVI_MediaInfo: Media status
  • CLU11: Display data

  Connectivity (1000ms):
  • TMU11: Telematics status
  • CUBIS11: Device status

  **Total Messages**: ~15 messages
  **ASIL Level**: QM
  **Feature**: Project-specific ambient lighting
end note

@enduml
